774
01:03:10.987 --> 01:03:12.956
"Cap. we got the guy. We got the guy."

775
01:03:12.956 --> 01:03:15.425
All right. All right. Send him on in.
I'm coming out.

776
01:03:15.425 --> 01:03:17.394
Okay. send him in. Let him go.

777
01:03:17.394 --> 01:03:19.396
(SPEAKING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

778
01:03:19.396 --> 01:03:20.864
- Let him go.
- Hey.

779
01:03:20.864 --> 01:03:22.766
Go. Send the captain out.

780
01:03:23.700 --> 01:03:25.602
All right. now. that handle. see?

781
01:03:25.602 --> 01:03:27.470
You're gonna wanna move that up and down.

782
01:03:27.804 --> 01:03:32.175
You gotta pump it. one. two. three.
four. five and then you drop.

783
01:03:32.175 --> 01:03:33.276
