Go back.

789
01:03:55.365 --> 01:03:56.733
Hey. Cap.

790
01:04:06.009 --> 01:04:07.410
Goddammit. No.

791
01:04:07.410 --> 01:04:09.112
- Goddammit.
- Dammit.

792
01:04:09.112 --> 01:04:10.213
- Cap.
- No.

793
01:04:10.213 --> 01:04:11.681
Sit. Sit.

794
01:04:11.681 --> 01:04:13.083
Here. Sit.

795
01:04:14.117 --> 01:04:15.185
Go.

796
01:04:21.424 --> 01:04:24.360
Irish. it's only us now.

797
01:04:42.412 --> 01:04:46.950
