at bset speed and intercept."

811
01:05:31.227 --> 01:05:33.830
"Further to follow. This is CTF 151 out."

812
01:05:36.499 --> 01:05:39.002
Ops. prep ScanEagle.
Need aerial surveillance.

813
01:05:39.002 --> 01:05:39.969
