It's a gift.

841
01:08:05.815 --> 01:08:06.849
Hey.

842
01:08:08.017 --> 01:08:09.285
(SPEAKING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

843
01:08:09.886 --> 01:08:10.820
Irish.

844
01:08:11.754 --> 01:08:14.891
You lie. Irish. Your ship no broke.

845
01:08:15.925 --> 01:08:17.260
They come Somalia too.

846
01:08:19.128 --> 01:08:20.096
More money.

847
01:08:31.207 --> 01:08:33.710
Looks like they're heading north
to the closest point of land.

848
01:08:35.945 --> 01:08:39.015
And that's only gonna take them 36 hours
at the most?

849
01:08:43.119 --> 01:08:45.188
Just gotta stay with them
till the Navy gets here.

850
01:09:01.037 --> 01:09:03.172
Give me some khat.

851
