Why? You've had more than your share.

852
01:09:05.808 --> 01:09:07.844
Says who? Give me some more.

853
01:09:07.844 --> 01:09:08.945
Shut up.

854
01:09:09.379 --> 01:09:10.947
Both of you. shut up.

855
01:09:11.614 --> 01:09:12.782
Just take it.

856
01:09:14.884 --> 01:09:15.952
This is it?

857
01:09:17.053 --> 01:09:19.722
- This is it?
- That's all I have.

858
01:09:19.722 --> 01:09:22.425
- Where is the rest?
- I don't have any.

859
01:09:23.059 --> 01:09:24.527
It's all gone.

860
01:09:24.527 --> 01:09:28.131
You are useless.
I should have taken it from you.

861
01:09:36.773 --> 01:09:39.175
Irish. it's taxes.

862
