You come to our waters. you got to pay.

864
01:09:48.951 --> 01:09:50.787
We were in international waters.

865
01:09:52.088 --> 01:09:53.656
Not your waters. international waters.

866
01:09:53.656 --> 01:09:57.060
We were carrying food
for starving people in Africa.

867
01:09:58.628 --> 01:10:00.163
Even Somalis.

868
01:10:00.163 --> 01:10:01.364
Yeah. sure.

869
01:10:02.031 --> 01:10:03.933
Rich countries like to help Somalis.

870
01:10:05.368 --> 01:10:06.836
Big ships come to our water...

871
01:10:09.238 --> 01:10:10.573
take all the fish out.

872
01:10:11.841 --> 01:10:14.944
- What's left for us to fish?
- So you're fishermen?

873
01:10:17.447 --> 01:10:18.748
Yeah. we're all fishermen.

874
01:10:27.857 --> 01:10:30.026
Hey. let me clean out that cut.

875
01:10:30.593 --> 01:10:32.862
Let me get the first-aid kit.
clean that out.

876
01:10:32.862 --> 01:10:34.363
It's gonna get infected.

877
01:10:34.363 --> 01:10:35.331
No.

878
