Well. how about the kid?
Can I look at his bare foot?

879
01:10:40.736 --> 01:10:41.704
No.

880
01:10:42.138 --> 01:10:43.673
They'll fix him when we get back.

881
01:10:44.207 --> 01:10:46.876
No. Come on. he's barefoot.
You three got sandals.

882
01:10:46.876 --> 01:10:49.011
He's got bare feet.

883
01:10:57.687 --> 01:10:58.788
Go ahead. go.

884
01:11:01.824 --> 01:11:02.859
All right.

885
01:11:05.595 --> 01:11:06.729
Just gonna get the kit.

886
01:11:39.729 --> 01:11:43.032
Go ahead. come here. It's all right.
Here. Your foot. Give me your foot.

887
01:11:43.900 --> 01:11:44.967
Come on.

888
01:11:46.002 --> 01:11:47.603
Let me see it. It's all right.

889
01:11:53.476 --> 01:11:57.213
How old are you. anyway?
What are you. 16. 17?

890
01:12:01.184 --> 01:12:03.653
You're too young to be out here
