891
01:12:03.653 --> 01:12:04.787
No talking.

892
01:12:05.421 --> 01:12:06.556
No talking.

893
01:12:20.369 --> 01:12:22.772
Hey. Hey.

894
01:12:22.772 --> 01:12:24.473
He's got a knife.

895
01:12:24.473 --> 01:12:26.943
