"The mothership is a Taiwanese fishing
trawler that was hijacked last year."

902
01:13:44.487 --> 01:13:45.788
"According to ONI's database..."

903
01:13:45.788 --> 01:13:49.759
"that vessel's under the control
of Somali warlord. Garaad."

904
01:13:49.759 --> 01:13:51.961
"We're working on getting the IDs
of the kidnappers."

905
01:13:52.495 --> 01:13:56.932
If this is Garaad's guys. they're looking
for a payday. which means they'll talk.

906
01:13:56.932 --> 01:14:00.436
If we can get them talking.
we can begin to wear them down. Over.

907
01:14:00.436 --> 01:14:03.139
"Frank. you need to know that
this thing is running big here..."

908
01:14:03.139 --> 01:14:04.874
"and there's a lot of pressure building."

909
