Stop being such an asshole.

932
01:16:29.185 --> 01:16:32.121
You've got to control him.

933
01:16:32.121 --> 01:16:33.722
Just drive and shut up.

934
01:16:34.657 --> 01:16:36.826
(SPEAKING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

935
01:16:37.493 --> 01:16:39.261
Hufan. can you hear me?

936
01:16:41.430 --> 01:16:42.565
Are you having trouble?

937
01:16:46.502 --> 01:16:49.638
No trouble. Irish. Slow piece of shit.

938
01:16:51.140 --> 01:16:53.542
Yeah. yeah. Shallow-draft.

939
01:16:54.743 --> 01:16:57.146
And you're fighting the current.
Gotta take that into account.

940
01:17:00.950 --> 01:17:02.218
I know what I'm doing.

941
01:17:04.053 --> 01:17:07.122
Yeah. yeah. sure. you do. Of course.
You're the captain now.

942
01:17:09.358 --> 01:17:10.359
Oh. hey. captain...

943
