why don't we open up that forward hatch
and get a little more air in here?

944
01:17:17.666 --> 01:17:19.301
What's wrong with you?

945
01:17:19.301 --> 01:17:20.603
Don't talk to me.

946
01:17:24.273 --> 01:17:26.642
A little air might do him some good.

947
01:17:34.316 --> 01:17:37.453
Yeah. open the hatch so your crew...

948
01:17:37.453 --> 01:17:40.956
no tricks. No. No tricks. Irish.

949
01:17:44.159 --> 01:17:46.428
Hufan. can you hear me?

950
01:17:47.062 --> 01:17:49.265
Hufan. can you hear me?

951
01:18:07.683 --> 01:18:09.285
We should be heading northwest.

952
01:18:10.553 --> 01:18:13.689
We've got to get to Garaad's port.

953
01:18:13.689 --> 01:18:16.358
I am but there's a lot of wind.

954
01:18:16.358 --> 01:18:19.662
- Just go.
- Okay. then let me do it.

955
01:18:19.662 --> 01:18:22.131
"Muse? Muse? Are you there?"

956
01:18:22.131 --> 01:18:23.766
"Muse? Are you there?"

957
01:18:27.503 --> 01:18:30.139
Hufan. where are you?

958
01:18:30.139 --> 01:18:32.408
"I'm having trouble with the engine."

959
01:18:33.175 --> 01:18:36.445
"Head home.
I'll be there as soon as I can."

960
01:18:36.946 --> 01:18:38.881
Hey. we're alone out here.

961
01:18:38.881 --> 01:18:41.050
We need you to pick us up.

962
01:18:41.050 --> 01:18:43.085
We've got to get out of this lifeboat.

963
01:18:43.085 --> 01:18:45.187
"Shut up and listen to me."

964
