966
01:18:58.567 --> 01:19:00.336
Sounds like there's a problem.
Is there a problem?

967
01:19:03.005 --> 01:19:04.039
Problem.

968
01:19:05.908 --> 01:19:07.209
No problem. Irish.

969
01:19:08.744 --> 01:19:10.479
Everything gonna be okay.

970
01:19:15.884 --> 01:19:18.821
(SEAL STAGING BASE - VIRGINIA)

971
01:19:19.755 --> 01:19:22.257
