Last year I took a Greek ship.

993
01:21:36.558 --> 01:21:37.826
Six million dollars.

994
01:21:40.028 --> 01:21:41.363
Six million dollars?

995
01:21:44.366 --> 01:21:45.601
So. what are you doing here?

996
01:21:51.573 --> 01:21:52.674
Shut up. Irish.

997
01:21:55.010 --> 01:21:56.011
Too much talk.

998
01:21:58.213 --> 01:22:01.950
Your problem isn't me talking to you.
Your problem is you not listening.

999
01:22:11.560 --> 01:22:12.394
Hey.

1000
01:22:12.394 --> 01:22:14.663
You think you have any power here?

1001
01:22:14.663 --> 01:22:18.500
- Let him go.
