01:59:34.901 --> 01:59:36.202
Andrea. I love you.

1497
01:59:37.570 --> 01:59:38.705
I love you. Ange.

1498
01:59:39.672 --> 01:59:40.707
Honey. I love you.

1499
01:59:42.575 --> 01:59:44.044
I love you. Danny. I'm sorry.

1500
01:59:44.644 --> 01:59:47.847
I'm sorry I'm here and not there with you.

1501
01:59:49.582 --> 01:59:53.086
"Can anybody hear this?
I can't stand this anymore."

1502
01:59:53.820 --> 01:59:54.788
One thirty metres.

1503
01:59:54.788 --> 01:59:56.056
That's 39 out from optimal.

1504
01:59:56.056 --> 01:59:58.358
Two red. No shot. We're still at two red.

1505
01:59:58.358 --> 02:00:02.062
I need sights on targets.
I need three targets green.

1506
02:00:05.598 --> 02:00:07.667
Don't kill him.

1507
02:00:07.667 --> 02:00:09.869
The elders are coming.

1508
02:00:09.869 --> 02:00:11.604
We will get our money.

1509
02:00:11.604 --> 02:00:13.606
You are both idiots.

1510
02:00:14.174 --> 02:00:16.242
No one is coming.

1511
02:00:23.650 --> 02:00:26.619
Alpha green. Bravo green.
Two green. one red.

1512
02:00:26.619 --> 02:00:29.956
- One twenty-one. Thirty metres out.
- "I can't take any more."

1513
02:00:29.956 --> 02:00:31.091
I'm all done.

1514
02:00:31.925 --> 02:00:32.859
I'm all done.

1515
02:00:33.626 --> 02:00:37.130
That's it.
We will all die if you kill him.

1516
02:00:37.130 --> 02:00:39.265
Everything they told you was a lie.

1517
02:00:40.300 --> 02:00:44.137
They will kill us all
and he is behind everything.

1518
02:00:44.137 --> 02:00:46.406
- One seventeen metres.
- Two green. one red.

1519
02:00:46.406 --> 02:00:49.409
- We do not have a shot.
- I need eyes on.

1520
02:00:49.409 --> 02:00:50.743
Sir. they're gonna shoot him.

1521
02:00:56.850 --> 02:00:59.686
- "Gun drawn. Gun drawn."
- Stop the tow.

1522
02:00:59.686 --> 02:01:01.020
"Roger. Stop the tow."

1523
02:01:04.424 --> 02:01:05.592
Execute.

1524
02:01:12.265 --> 02:01:13.466
What was that?

1525
02:01:48.568 --> 02:01:50.370
Oh. no.

1526
02:02:16.596 --> 02:02:17.997
We're gonna get you out of here
and get you home.

1527
02:02:24.571 --> 02:02:26.906
"Take him down. Take him down.
The hostage is safe."

1528
02:02:26.906 --> 02:02:28.074
Get down.

1529
02:02:28.975 --> 02:02:30.176
- Put your head down.
- What?

1530
02:02:31.544 --> 02:02:34.080
- Good job. guys. We got them.
- Three Tangos down.

1531
02:02:34.514 --> 02:02:37.617
Captain Phillips is safe and en route.
Bainbridge. over.

1532
02:02:37.617 --> 02:02:38.818
Well done. everybody.

1533
02:02:38.818 --> 02:02:41.554
- Right here. Go to this guy right here.
- Come with me. captain.

1534
02:02:43.289 --> 02:02:44.324
You just sit down.

1535
02:02:45.925 --> 02:02:47.760
Are you okay? Are you okay?

1536
02:02:56.669 --> 02:02:57.704
This way.

1537
02:03:01.174 --> 02:03:02.575
- Watch your step.
- Step.

1538
02:03:07.480 --> 02:03:08.815
Careful. sir.

1539
02:03:12.318 --> 02:03:14.153
Welcome aboard. These guys
are gonna take you straight to medical...

1540
02:03:14.153 --> 02:03:15.355
and get you checked out.

1541
02:03:16.656 --> 02:03:19.492
HM-1. he has impact injuries.
He's in shock.

1542
02:03:19.892 --> 02:03:21.728
Okay. Are you able to walk okay. sir?

1543
02:03:22.528 --> 02:03:27.066
- Are you okay? What's your name?
- Rich. Rich Phillips.

1544
02:03:29.602 --> 02:03:33.006
We're gonna turn you over to the United
States Department of Justice.

1545
02:03:33.006 --> 02:03:34.807
You're going to America to face trial.

1546
02:03:36.576 --> 02:03:37.644
You shoot my friends?

1547
02:03:38.511 --> 02:03:41.281
Captain Phillips is free.
All of your friends are dead.

1548
02:03:43.182 --> 02:03:45.151
It's over. You're going to America now.

1549
02:03:46.653 --> 02:03:49.022
You have been suspected
of piracy operations.

1550
02:03:49.022 --> 02:03:50.423
I am now gonna read you your rights.

1551
02:03:51.724 --> 02:03:54.294
You have the right to remain silent
and make no statement at all.

1552
02:03:55.161 --> 02:03:58.298
Any statement you do. may or can be used
against you in judicial proceedings.

1553
02:04:02.435 --> 02:04:03.836
Captain Phillips. please come in.

1554
02:04:05.872 --> 02:04:06.773
Have a seat.

1555
02:04:08.107 --> 02:04:09.108
Trauma shears.

1556
02:04:10.443 --> 02:04:12.745
I'm Chief O'Brien.
I'll be your corpsman today. okay?

1557
02:04:12.745 --> 02:04:14.480
Can you please tell me what's going on?

1558
02:04:16.249 --> 02:04:17.116
Can you talk?

1559
02:04:18.184 --> 02:04:20.086
- Can you tell me what's going on?
- Yeah.

1560
02:04:21.454 --> 02:04:22.455
I'm okay.

1561
02:04:22.455 --> 02:04:24.057
Are you okay? Because you don't look okay.

1562
02:04:24.957 --> 02:04:26.326
Are you in any pain right now?

1563
02:04:28.828 --> 02:04:30.229
Are you in pain right now?

1564
02:04:31.331 --> 02:04:32.665
Right there. on your side.

1565
02:04:33.132 --> 02:04:34.901
Okay. Let me see it really quick.

1566
02:04:34.901 --> 02:04:37.070
Can you lift up your arm a little bit?
Does that hurt?

1567
02:04:37.737 --> 02:04:38.671
- Little bit?
- Little bit.

1568
02:04:38.671 --> 02:04:41.307
Okay. Is it tender?
Go ahead and put your arm down.

1569
02:04:41.307 --> 02:04:43.743
Okay. I need you to look at me.
I need you to calm down...

1570
02:04:43.743 --> 02:04:46.379
and I need you to breathe.
There you go. Deep breaths.

1571
02:04:46.379 --> 02:04:47.814
There you go. Very good.

1572
02:04:48.281 --> 02:04:50.516
Awesome.
Now I want you to relax your arm.

1573
02:04:50.516 --> 02:04:52.218
Okay. We're gonna put this little thing
on your finger...

1574
02:04:52.218 --> 02:04:54.120
and we're gonna get your heart rate
and your oxygen level...

1575
02:04:54.120 --> 02:04:55.955
- make sure you're breathing okay.
- Okay.

1576
02:04:55.955 --> 02:04:58.024
I want you to keep doing that. okay?

1577
02:04:58.024 --> 02:04:59.692
- Gonna put this on your finger.
- What happened to your head?

1578
02:05:00.660 --> 02:05:02.428
Captain. can you tell me
what happened to your head?

1579
02:05:02.428 --> 02:05:03.396
Put it on your finger.

1580
02:05:05.431 --> 02:05:06.332
They...

1581
02:05:09.569 --> 02:05:11.404
It's okay. take your time. take your time.

1582
02:05:11.404 --> 02:05:14.107
There's a two centimetre laceration
on the left eyebrow.

1583
02:05:15.908 --> 02:05:17.710
It's okay. It's all right.

1584
02:05:17.710 --> 02:05:19.112
- Okay. Okay.
- It's okay.

1585
02:05:19.112 --> 02:05:21.280
I want you to look at me
and I want you to breathe.

1586
02:05:21.280 --> 02:05:22.515
- Do you understand?
- Yeah. Yeah.

1587
02:05:22.515 --> 02:05:23.950
Okay. all right.

1588
02:05:23.950 --> 02:05:25.485
He's got a four centimetre gap.

1589
02:05:26.652 --> 02:05:28.855
Little laceration there
on the left temple.

1590
02:05:28.855 --> 02:05:30.056
- Got it.
- Okay. Very good.

1591
02:05:30.056 --> 02:05:31.724
All right. You're doing great. okay?

1592
02:05:32.425 --> 02:05:34.927
Did all this blood
come from your eyebrow and your head?

1593
02:05:36.796 --> 02:05:38.197
- What?
- Did all the blood...

1594
02:05:38.197 --> 02:05:40.700
come from your eyebrow right here
and on your head?

1595
02:05:40.700 --> 02:05:43.002
- All of this.
- Well. not. no. not all of it.

1596
02:05:43.002 --> 02:05:44.637
- Okay.
- That's not mine.

1597
02:05:45.405 --> 02:05:47.306
Okay. all right. all right. Look at me.

1598
02:05:48.274 --> 02:05:49.842
- Okay. We're gonna lay you down. Okay?
- Okay.

1599
02:05:49.842 --> 02:05:51.177
- All right.
- Yeah. Yeah.

1600
02:05:52.645 --> 02:05:55.114
I want you to lay down nice and gently.
Nice and gently.

1601
02:05:55.114 --> 02:05:57.049
You're okay. You're okay. I got you.

1602
02:05:58.484 --> 02:06:00.420
There you go. Very good.

1603
02:06:01.354 --> 02:06:02.955
Captain. you're safe now. okay?

1604
02:06:02.955 --> 02:06:04.524
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

1605
02:06:05.758 --> 02:06:07.460
- You're okay.
- Thank you.

1606
02:06:07.460 --> 02:06:08.361
You're welcome.

1607
02:06:09.295 --> 02:06:12.565
- Does my family know?
- Your family knows you're safe.

1608
02:06:12.565 --> 02:06:15.001
You'll be able to call them
as soon as you are taken care of.

1609
02:06:18.438 --> 02:06:20.239
Sir. I need you to breathe. okay?

1610
02:06:20.573 --> 02:06:22.375
You are safe and you are fine.

1611
02:06:23.910 --> 02:06:24.977
It's gonna be okay.

1612
02:06:26.846 --> 02:06:28.247
Everything's gonna be okay.

1613
02:06:30.650 --> 02:06:31.951
It's gonna be okay.

1614
02:07:13.426 --> 02:07:18.965
(RICHARD PHILLIPS RETURNED TO VERMONT ON APRIL 17. 2009
AND WAS REUNITED WITH HIS FAMILY.)

1615
02:07:18.965 --> 02:07:22.235
(ABDUWALI MUSE WAS CONVICTED OF PIRACY)

1616
02:07:22.235 --> 02:07:26.973
(AND IS CURRENTLY SERVING 33 YEARS AT THE
FEDERAL CORRECTIONAL COMPLEX. TERRE HAUTE. INDIANA.)

1617
02:07:26.973 --> 02:07:32.178
(ON JULY 25. 2010.
CAPTAIN PHILLIPS WENT BACK TO SEA.)
